@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Kia Syros Mid Diesel Automatic: The Value-for-Money Champion";
}
@section MetaTags {
    <meta name="keywords" content="Kia Syros, Kia Syros Mid Diesel Automatic, value-for-money SUV, best compact SUV, Kia Syros pricing, diesel SUV India" />
    <meta name="description" content="Discover why the Kia Syros Mid Diesel Automatic is the best value-for-money variant. Dive into its features, performance, and pricing to see what makes it a standout choice in the compact SUV segment." />
}
<body id="bg">
    @* <div class="header-img"><img src="~/images/main-slider/header.webp" alt="Header Image" /></div> *@
    <div class="blog-main-container m-t90">
        <div class="latest-bikes-details-content">
            <h3 class="subheading">Kia Syros : Value-for-Money Variant</h3>
            <div class="row m-b20">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center">
                    <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/headerimage.webp" alt="headerimage" title="headerimage" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>After analyzing the features and price, the <b>Mid Diesel Automatic</b> variant stands out as the value-for-money option. Priced at <b>₹11,49,000,</b> it offers a balanced mix of premium features like the 10.25-inch infotainment system, advanced safety features, and exceptional mileage of 21 km/l, making it an excellent choice for families and frequent travelers.</p>
            <h3 class="subheading">Key Highlights of the Mid Diesel Automatic Variant</h3>
            <div>
                <h5 class="subheading">1.Power and Performance</h5>
                <div class="row m-b20">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/engine2.webp" alt="engine" title="engine"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/rooftop.webp" alt="rooftop" title="rooftop" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>Equipped with a 1.5L diesel engine, this variant delivers an impressive<b> 120 PS of power</b> and<b> 250 Nm of torque.</b> The 6-speed automatic transmission ensures a smooth driving experience, whether in city traffic or on highways.</p>
                <h5 class="subheading">2.Outstanding Fuel Efficiency</h5>
                <div class="row m-b20">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/buttons.webp" alt="buttons" title="buttons" />
                      </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/airbags.webp" alt="airbags" title="airbags" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p>With an ARAI-certified mileage of<b> 21 km/l,</b> this variant is ideal for those seeking cost-effective long drives without compromising on performance.</p>
                <h5 class="subheading">3.Advanced Safety Features</h5>
                <p>Safety remains a priority with features like:</p>             
                <ul>
                    <li>Airbags</li>
                    <li>ABS with EBD</li>
                    <li>Electronic Stability Control (ESC)</li>
                    <li>Hill Start Assist</li>
                </ul>
                <h5 class="subheading">4.Infotainment and Connectivity</h5>              
                <p>The 10.25-inch touchscreen infotainment system with <span class="font-weight-700">Android Auto </span> and <span class="font-weight-700">Apple CarPlay </span> ensures seamless connectivity and entertainment during your journeys.</p>
                <div class="row m-b20">
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center">
                        <img src="~/images/valueformoney/2025/jan/kiasyrosspecs/front.webp" alt="front" title="front" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h5 class="subheading">5.Comfort and Convenience</h5>
                <p>Enjoy features like:</p>               
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Ventilated Seats</span> for enhanced comfort in all seasons.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Automatic Climate Control</span> to maintain an ideal cabin temperature.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Premium Upholstery </span>that adds a touch of luxury.</li>
                </ul>

            </div>

            <div class="div-line"></div>
            <h3 class="subheading">Price Comparison</h3>
            <div style="overflow-x: auto;">
                <table class="comparison-table-content">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="text-center">Variant</th>
                            <th class="text-center">Price (Ex-showroom)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>Base Diesel Manual</td>
                            <td>₹9,49,000</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><span class="text-highlight">Mid Diesel Automatic</span></td>
                            <td><span class="text-highlight">₹11,49,000</span></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="compare-head-text">
                            <td>Top Diesel Automatic</td>
                            <td>₹12,99,000</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p>For just <b>₹2,00,000</b> more than the base diesel manual, the mid variant offers automatic transmission and several additional features, making it a smart investment.</p>
            <h3 class="subheading">Why Choose the Mid Diesel Automatic?</h3>
            <div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-weight-700">Ideal for Families and Frequent Travelers:</span> The spacious cabin, excellent fuel economy, and advanced safety features make it perfect for long-distance journeys.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-weight-700">Value-Packed Features:</span> It includes premium amenities typically reserved for higher variants at a much more affordable price.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="font-weight-700">Low Maintenance Costs:</span> Diesel engines are known for their durability and cost efficiency, adding to the long-term value of this variant.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>     
        <p>Click Here For <a class="for-link" asp-controller="ValueForMoney" asp-action="KiaSyros_2">Features & Specifications of Kia Syros</a></p>         
    </div>
    </div>
</body>